name: Leapord Print Hobo Bag
description:
Fabric bag good for a purse, school bag or reusable shopping bag. Tie handle and bright bold pattern. Large enough to hold a big book but flexible enough to be folded into another bag

Measurements
10" wide, 12" tall from bottom to opening and 22.5" from top of handle to the bottom of the bag

name: Turqoise Flower Print Hobo Bag
description:
This Hobo has a large floral print with a turquoise lining. It is big enough to hold books or whatever you want but it folds up really small for travel or being used as a shopping bag.

Measurements
10" wide, 21" from bottom to opening and 22.5" from top of the strap to bottom of the bag

name: Red Stripe Hobo Bag
description:
This Hobo is cotton with textured lining for a sturdy construction. It ties at the top and is large enough to fit a big book but flexible enough to be folded into another bag to be used as a shopping bag. It's really handy and versatile I use the one I have all the time

Measurements
10" wide, 12" tall from bottom to opening and 22" from bottom of the bag to the top of the handle

name: Blue Paisly Print Hobo Bag
description:
This Hobo has a really nice blue print on it. It's tie top makes it unique and it is large enough to hold everything you need, including books. It is also flexible enough to fold into another bag for travel or to be used as a shopping bag.

Measurements
10" wide, 12" from bottom to opening and 22.5" from the top of the strap to the bottom of the bag

name: Red Vine on White Hobo Bag
description:
This white hobo has a really nice print of red trees and vines on it. It has a thick tan lining for stability but it's still flexible enough to fold up well for travel or use as a shopping bag. It's large enough to hold books and has a tie strap. 

Measurements
10" wide, 12" from bottom to opening and 22.5" from top of strap to bottom of bag
